drm/arcpgu: Opt in debugfs

This change adopts debugfs usage for outputting useful data.
As of today we print:
 * Mode and real HW clock values
 * Standard FB info

Code is heavily borrowed from ARM's HDLCD thus adding Liviu in Cc.

